    "body": "proof-of-concept [here](https://github.com/klutzy/rust/commit/8d68093435133873c1ab30295b91b01d7ffaf3bc). This passes `check-stage1-{rpass, rfail, cfail, rmake}` and seems to work well?\nFor end-users, the only change is that the program doesn't print `task '<main>' has overflowed its stack` message but just dies, and it leaves SIGSEGV instead of SIGILL.\n",
