    "created_at": "2014-06-08T06:38:37Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-06-08T06:38:37Z",
    "body": "I do agree, however, that I think the segmented stack prelude may be causing more trouble than it's worth now. I suspect, but have never confirmed, that this is not helping FreeBSD by having segmented stacks enabled.\n",
