    "created_at": "2014-07-09T21:34:59Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-07-09T21:34:59Z",
    "body": "By using SEH exceptions handling we'd be able to catch this exact exception and call library code instead of merely causing a SIGSEGV.\n",
